Southern Cross Seeks Extension on Debt Facility, Telegraph Says

-- B y   P a u l   D o b s o n
-- 
2011-06-19T09:36:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-19/southern-cross-seeks-extension-on-debt-facility-telegraph-says.html
Southern Cross Healthcare Plc is in
talks with lenders to extend debt covenant waivers on its loans
to the end of October from the end of June, the Sunday Telegraph
reported, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
